03:17.629 --> 03:19.918
My invoice is in the envelope,
if that's all.

03:20.590 --> 03:22.665
Yes, Mr. Welles. Thank you.

03:23.259 --> 03:26.710
Senator, let me know if I can be
of further assistance to you.

03:26.970 --> 03:28.594
I'll be in touch.

04:06.175 --> 04:07.550
Hello?

04:08.093 --> 04:09.552
You're home.

04:10.345 --> 04:11.970
We're back here.

04:13.182 --> 04:14.047
How did it go?

04:14.308 --> 04:15.387
I think very well.

04:15.642 --> 04:16.805
Good.

04:17.101 --> 04:19.011
Daddy's home, sweetie.

04:20.232 --> 04:22.308
How's the textbook business?

04:23.194 --> 04:26.693
I got 10,000 words on
the FederaI Theatre project.

04:26.947 --> 04:30.281
